    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《九霄仙途》</strong>是一款融合了深度策略构筑与佛系挂机养成的国风修仙RPG。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，修仙不仅仅是提升等级，更是对“灵阵”的精心推演与五行法则的极致运用。采集灵材、开辟洞府、炼丹锻器，从一介凡人一步步渡劫飞升，成就无上大道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【自动或手动自由切换的放置策略战斗】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握元素属性（火、水、风、土）与光暗的相生相克法则。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗采用自动回合制，角色将自动释放神通与绝技。你需要合理安排队伍的配置，利用属性克制打出成吨的伤害，或是在敌人的狂暴攻击下生存下来。<br>遇到高难度强度，还可以切换手动模式合理安排技能以精准制敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/081ed58cb9b34c5fb74259b4f80b484c.poster.avif?t=1771246637\" width=640 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/081ed58cb9b34c5fb74259b4f80b484c.webm?t=1771246637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/081ed58cb9b34c5fb74259b4f80b484c.mp4?t=1771246637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【核心玩法：灵阵构筑】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >告别枯燥的战力堆砌。本作的核心战力来源于“灵阵”系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要收集并强化上百种不同的法宝，将它们填入12个阵眼之中。每件法宝都拥有独特的词条技能（如：攻击提升、暴击加成、背水一战等）。如何根据敌人的属性，搭配出一套完美的法宝盘，是战胜强敌的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/f08ce25207012492d9312fcdefa2a6bd.poster.avif?t=1771246637\" width=1170 height=772 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/f08ce25207012492d9312fcdefa2a6bd.webm?t=1771246637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/f08ce25207012492d9312fcdefa2a6bd.mp4?t=1771246637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【洞府经营与生活技能】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修仙不只是打打杀杀，还有人情世故与生产经营。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集：派遣人手前往深山矿洞，获取灵木与玄铁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵植：在药园种植稀世仙草，这是炼制渡劫丹药的唯一来源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >炼丹与锻造：亲自开炉炼丹，或打造绝世神兵。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管事系统：结识的道友不仅能上阵杀敌，还能被任命为建筑管事，大幅提升生产效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/30c9aefea0f71bc0daa8bf24f1e9b49e.poster.avif?t=1771246637\" width=1170 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/30c9aefea0f71bc0daa8bf24f1e9b49e.webm?t=1771246637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/30c9aefea0f71bc0daa8bf24f1e9b49e.mp4?t=1771246637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/913d87a445ad84217fe947f54a45610d.poster.avif?t=1771246637\" width=1170 height=414 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/913d87a445ad84217fe947f54a45610d.webm?t=1771246637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/913d87a445ad84217fe947f54a45610d.mp4?t=1771246637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【逆天改命，渡劫飞升】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在该游戏中，即使是R级的普通角色，也能通过“渡劫”系统逆天改命，晋升为SSR甚至UR品质！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集素材，炼制丹药，帮助你的道友突破境界瓶颈。没有废卡，只有未成长的潜力股。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/4770f6f5c8164b21e212846aa71b6ea7.avif?t=1771246637\" width=1560 height=868 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【无限扩展的模组支持】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内置了强大的 Mod 制作与管理工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以轻松创建属于自己的角色、法宝、敌人，甚至编写全新的剧情事件。通过 Steam 创意工坊，与其他修仙者分享你的创意，或下载他人的模组，让修仙世界无限扩张。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/bf96397d5f116dc3a45797b8ecc6feb9.poster.avif?t=1771246637\" width=1170 height=729 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1580820/extras/bf96397d5f116dc3a45797b8ecc6feb9.webm?t=1771246637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>踏入九霄，即刻开始你的挂机修仙之旅！</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>官方交流Q群：1030892619<br>有什么游戏上的疑问或者建议和BUG反馈，都可以加群交流！</strong></h2>",
